People ex rel. James, Appellant, v. Gilon et al., Assessors, Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 28, 1890.) Appeal from special term, New York county.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

*943Truman H. Baldwin, for appellant. G. L. Sterling, for respondents. Van Brunt, P. J.

The case of People v. Same Defendants, ante, 690, {decided herewith,) disposes of the questions involved in this appeal. The order should be affirmed, without costs. All concur.
